        "title": "Term 1",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "receuww8O1mJn6cVL",
            "term": 1,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] Check out [this video](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AJBBVQrRwqo) for a deeper look at the history of cartography.\n[ ] View the Activity Section on page 9-10 of _Mapping the World with Art. _You can make a navigational quadrant and use it at night to find Polaris.\n[ ] View a [video](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OUYTG8cGtRI) on the difference between digital and paper maps"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 2,
        "title": "Term 2",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "recslbjCms7Cdevmo",
            "term": 2,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] Watch these videos about the different continents you're studying: [Americas](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfM2lZq63hc&list=PLvJNSf-7NfrMjdMvjxg0eWJnV3yDPN_zn&index=5), [Asia](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cInBgbH7UYw&list=PLvJNSf-7NfrMjdMvjxg0eWJnV3yDPN_zn&index=2), and [Europe](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cJt5Yi48oQ0).\n[ ] Try these [classic Canadian recipes](https://canadianfoodfocus.org/in-your-kitchen/classic-canadian-dishes/) from the provinces you are studying. \n[ ] With a teacher's permission, watch some of the bay and harbour [webcams](https://tourismtofino.com/plan-your-trip/weather-webcams/) located in Tofino on Vancouver Island."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 3,
        "title": "Term 3",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "rec56XN68JSLBG2vq",
            "term": 3,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] [Watch this video ](https://youtu.be/51MqSCZ7si8?si=hKYWCj7ZsFTUUqiJ)from the Canadian Geographic Challenge National Final and see how many questions you can answer. \n[ ] Create a geography trivia game based on what you've learned so far this year. Challenge your family or class to see how many questions they can answer correctly. \n[ ] [Watch this video](https://youtu.be/M6TtQTsVlTY?si=JEJ-XfWveHucq2SP) on Nunavut: Canada's Unbelievable Ancient Landscapes"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
